content: Non-Void is an optional miniboss fight, and one of Yellowbrow's four disciples that you can encounter in Chapter 3 of Black Myth Wukong. The target of a Snow Fox's revenge and questline you can undertake, Non-Void hides within the New Thunderclap Temple.
